flowchart LR
    subgraph EntryPoints[Entry points]
        A1[LinkedIn profile click-through]
        A2[Resume or application link]
        A3[Interview follow-up leave-behind]
        A4[Networking or referral share]
    end

    EntryPoints --> B[Visitor lands on career.digiscott.com]

    B --> C[Homepage gives concise positioning]
    C --> D{What does the visitor need next?}

    D -->|Fast scan| E[Confirm role fit and credibility]
    D -->|Evidence| F[Explore use cases]
    D -->|Deeper context| G[Ask AI Career Advocate]
    D -->|Next step| H[Contact Scott]

    E --> I[Download resume or open LinkedIn]
    F --> J[Review problem, approach, artifacts, and outcomes]
    G --> K[Ask about experience, strengths, projects, or fit]

    I --> L[Visitor gains confidence]
    J --> L
    K --> L

    L --> M{Ready to continue?}
    M -->|Yes| N[Email, phone, LinkedIn, referral, or interview request]
    M -->|Not yet| O[Return later with a clearer picture of Scott's value]